snippet.title: Fans made a campaign to prevent Amber Heard appears in “Aquaman 2”
snippet.description:
Fans made a campaign to prevent Amber Heard appears in “Aquaman 2”. 
A controversial petition are taking to the social networks these days, and it has to do directly with the followers of the tapes of superheroes. And is that fans of Aquaman are collecting signatures for that Amber Heard does not appear in the upcoming movie of hero water.

“Please Like and Subscribe to my channel and click the bell icon to get new video updates.”
Stay at home, Save lives.
